item.title: CVE-2017-1194|2024-08-05T13:25:17.482Z -- ibm%20corporation -- ibm%20websphere%20application%20server
item.description: IBM WebSphere Application Server 7.0, 8.0, 8.5, and 9.0 is vulnerable to cross-site request forgery which could allow an attacker to execute malicious and unauthorized actions transmitted from a user that the website trusts. IBM X-Force ID: 123669.
